On 1/2/04 5:26 PM, "dogsbody" <dogsbody(-at-)telus.net> wrote:

> Good day all,
> 1977 2.0 bus: Does any one know if there are different alternator brackets
> for the different displacement type 4 bus engines?

Yes. 

72-74 and 79 have one style, 75-78 have another style. If you switch exhaust
you have to get the appropriate bracket.

